values and continue what our ancestors left behind ratan tata ethics values ancestors the day i am not able to fly will be a sad day for me ratan tata sad day i am i will certainly not join politics i would like to be remembered as a clean businessman who has not partaken in any twists and turns beneath the surface and one who has been reasonably successful ratan tata politics successful clean power and wealth are not two of my main stakes ratan tata power wealth two i would say that one of the things i wish i could do differently would be to be more outgoing ratan tata wish more i wish i followed someone who had very large shoes he had very large shoes mr j r d tata he was a legend in the indian business community he had been at the helm of the tata organization for  years you were almost starting to think he was going to be there forever ratan tata business community shoes i have two or three cars that i like but today ferrari would be the best car i have driven in terms of being an impressive car ratan tata car best today i may have hurt some people along the way but i would like to be seen as somebody who has done his best to do the right thing for any situation and not compromised ratan tata best hurt people when you see in places like africa and parts of asia abject poverty hungry children and malnutrition around you and you look at yourself as being people who have well being and comforts i think it takes a very insensitive tough person not to feel they need to do something ratan tata children yourself poverty telco is totally committed to commercial vehicles where it is bound to remain a major player what may well happen in the future is we may split the company into two business units ratan tata business future company i think there are many honest businessmen ratan tata think honest businessmen banana republics are run on cronyism ratan tata banana run republics people of great power wield great power but people of lesser power or people who have fallen out of power go to jail without adequate evidence or their bodies are found in the trunks of cars ratan tata power great people people still believe what they read is necessarily the truth ratan tata truth believe people what are the crumple zones on scooters the helmet is the only crumple zone i can think of ratan tata think i can only challenges need to be given to an organization ratan tata challenges organization some entrepreneurs talk of a high burn rate high advertising rate and so on with no outcome so it doesnt impress me but an entrepreneur who has that kind of a feeling of responsibility towards his investors is somebody who will have all my support ratan tata support responsibility me i buy a lot of electronics some which i never take out of the box ratan tata box never electronics if i were to look in the united states or in europe in some of the garages you would have a bentley or two bentleys or a highend mercedes and you may find a smart also in that same garage because that person thinks its a fun extra car to have he may have four cars but also have a smart because he thinks it is cute ratan tata car smart fun i would say that im blessed with a very very good executive team that operates reasonably autonomously each of the companies ratan tata team good blessed the early rockefellers made their wealth from being in certain businesses and remained personally very wealthy ratan tata wealth early being the economic situation the high cost of undertaking manufacturing the supply chain  which is by the way dying out also as manufacturing undergoes hardship  make the uk not the first place you would look at to make a manufacturing investment ratan tata look you dying share this page cite this page citation find on amazon ratan tata related authors naveen jain azim premji mukesh ambani vijay mallya kumar mangalam birla mohnish pabrai cyrus s poonawalla dhirubhai ambani brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures